{
  "info": {
    "name": "CryptoNest API",
    "_postman_id": "cryptonest-api-collection",
    "description": "Complete API documentation for CryptoNest – a Crypto Portfolio Tracker with JWT Authentication and Role-Based Access Control.\n\n## Base URL\n`http://localhost:5000/api/v1`\n\n## Authentication\nMost routes require a Bearer token in the Authorization header:\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer <your_jwt_token>\n```\n\n## Roles\n- **user** – Can manage their own portfolio\n- **admin** – Can view all users' portfolios",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:5000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "JWT token – auto-set after login/register"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "User registration, login, and profile endpoints.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register User",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token saved:', res.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123\",\n  \"role\": \"user\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Register a new user. Passwords are hashed with bcrypt before storage.\n\n**Roles:** `user` (default) or `admin`\n\n**Password rules:** Minimum 6 characters.\n\n**Auto-saves JWT token** to the collection variable `token` via test script."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "201 – Success",
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"User registered successfully\",\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": \"64abc123\",\n    \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n    \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n    \"role\": \"user\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "400 – Email Already Registered",
              "status": "Bad Request",
              "code": 400,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Email already registered\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login User",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token saved:', res.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Authenticate an existing user and receive a JWT token (valid for 7 days).\n\n**Auto-saves JWT token** to the collection variable `token` via test script."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 – Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Login successful\",\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": \"64abc123\",\n    \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n    \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n    \"role\": \"user\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "401 – Invalid Credentials",
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Invalid email or password\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Fetch the currently authenticated user's profile.\n\n**Requires:** Bearer token in Authorization header."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 – Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"user\": {\n    \"_id\": \"64abc123\",\n    \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n    \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n    \"role\": \"user\",\n    \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "401 – No Token",
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Not authorized, no token\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Coins (Portfolio)",
      "description": "CRUD operations for the authenticated user's crypto portfolio.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Add Coin",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"symbol\": \"BTC\",\n  \"name\": \"Bitcoin\",\n  \"quantity\": 0.5,\n  \"buyPrice\": 42000,\n  \"notes\": \"Long-term hold\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/coins",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["coins"]
            },
            "description": "Add a new coin to the authenticated user's portfolio.\n\n**Required fields:** `symbol`, `name`, `quantity`, `buyPrice`\n\n**Optional:** `notes`\n\n**Requires:** Bearer token."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "201 – Coin Added",
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Coin added\",\n  \"coin\": {\n    \"_id\": \"64def456\",\n    \"user\": \"64abc123\",\n    \"symbol\": \"BTC\",\n    \"name\": \"Bitcoin\",\n    \"quantity\": 0.5,\n    \"buyPrice\": 42000,\n    \"notes\": \"Long-term hold\",\n    \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "500 – Validation Error",
              "status": "Internal Server Error",
              "code": 500,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Coin symbol is required\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Coins",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/coins",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["coins"]
            },
            "description": "Retrieve all coins in the authenticated user's portfolio, sorted by most recently added.\n\nEach coin includes a calculated `totalInvested` field (`quantity × buyPrice`).\n\n**Requires:** Bearer token."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 – Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"count\": 2,\n  \"portfolio\": [\n    {\n      \"_id\": \"64def456\",\n      \"symbol\": \"BTC\",\n      \"name\": \"Bitcoin\",\n      \"quantity\": 0.5,\n      \"buyPrice\": 42000,\n      \"totalInvested\": 21000,\n      \"notes\": \"Long-term hold\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"_id\": \"64def789\",\n      \"symbol\": \"ETH\",\n      \"name\": \"Ethereum\",\n      \"quantity\": 2,\n      \"buyPrice\": 2500,\n      \"totalInvested\": 5000,\n      \"notes\": \"\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-02T00:00:00.000Z\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Coin",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"quantity\": 1.0,\n  \"buyPrice\": 40000,\n  \"notes\": \"Added more at dip\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/coins/:id",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["coins", ":id"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "64def456",
                  "description": "MongoDB ObjectId of the coin"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Update a coin entry. Only the owner of the coin can update it.\n\n**Path param:** `:id` – MongoDB ObjectId of the coin\n\n**Requires:** Bearer token. Must be the coin owner."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 – Updated",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Coin updated\",\n  \"coin\": {\n    \"_id\": \"64def456\",\n    \"symbol\": \"BTC\",\n    \"name\": \"Bitcoin\",\n    \"quantity\": 1.0,\n    \"buyPrice\": 40000,\n    \"notes\": \"Added more at dip\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "403 – Not Authorized",
              "status": "Forbidden",
              "code": 403,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Not authorized\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "404 – Coin Not Found",
              "status": "Not Found",
              "code": 404,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Coin not found\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Coin",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/coins/:id",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["coins", ":id"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "64def456",
                  "description": "MongoDB ObjectId of the coin"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Delete a coin from the portfolio. Only the owner can delete their own coin.\n\n**Path param:** `:id` – MongoDB ObjectId of the coin\n\n**Requires:** Bearer token. Must be the coin owner."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 – Deleted",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Coin removed from portfolio\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "403 – Not Authorized",
              "status": "Forbidden",
              "code": 403,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Not authorized\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin",
      "description": "Admin-only endpoints. Requires role: `admin`.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get All Users' Coins",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/coins/admin/all",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["coins", "admin", "all"]
            },
            "description": "Fetch all coins across all users. Each coin is populated with the owner's name, email, and role.\n\n**Requires:** Bearer token with `admin` role.\n\nReturns 403 if a non-admin user attempts access."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 – Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"count\": 3,\n  \"coins\": [\n    {\n      \"_id\": \"64def456\",\n      \"symbol\": \"BTC\",\n      \"name\": \"Bitcoin\",\n      \"quantity\": 0.5,\n      \"buyPrice\": 42000,\n      \"user\": {\n        \"_id\": \"64abc123\",\n        \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n        \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n        \"role\": \"user\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "403 – Admins Only",
              "status": "Forbidden",
              "code": 403,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Access denied: Admins only\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
